<?xml version="1.0"?>
<html>
<head><title>Oracc Volume Template Generator</title><base href="http://oracc.museum.upenn.edu/doc/wwwhome/util/"/></head>
<body>
  <h2>Oracc Volume Template Generator</h2>
  <p>This form creates lists of place-holders for catalog entries.</p>
  <p>Give the name of the volume in the 'Volume' field.</p>
  <p>Give the start and end page/plate numbers in the From/To fields;
  these must be in arabic digits.  You may give leading zeroes if you want
  them in the output.</p>
  <p>To get roman numerals click the relevant radio-button.</p>
  <p>The output is sent to the current browser window--simply
  select-all then cut and paste it to a file.</p>
  <p>A &lt;TAB&gt; character is included at the end of each line to make it easy 
  to add a field at the end.</p>
  <hr/>
  <form method="POST" action="/voltemplate">
    <input type="hidden" name="cgimode" value="1"/>
    <table>
      <tr><td>Volume:</td><td><input type="text" name="prefix" size="20"/></td></tr>
      <tr><td>From:</td><td><input type="text" name="from" size="4"/></td></tr>
      <tr><td>To:</td><td><input type="text" name="to" size="4"/></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Owner:</td><td><input type="text" name="owner" size="20"/></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Genre:</td><td><input type="text" name="genre" size="20"/></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Period:</td><td><input type="text" name="period" size="20"/></td></tr>
      <tr>
	<td>Numbers:</td>
	<td>
	  <input type="radio" name="nums" value="arabic" checked="checked"/> Arabic; 
	  <input type="radio" name="nums" value="roman"/> roman (lowercase);
	  <input type="radio" name="nums" value="Roman"/> Roman (uppercase).
	</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <p><input type="submit" value="Create template"/></p>
  </form>
  <hr/>
</body>
</html>
